Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fs42\fad(300,300)}{\move(720,60,720,8)}{\blur3}字幕重校、压制：巴洛克哥特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么你已经做好参加考试的准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你想 我也拍拍你的马屁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们今后要在我们认为最合适的环境里努力学习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}缀命之炼金术师?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肖·塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}进行生体炼成的第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这样 我们直到考试前都在塔克家里度过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人没有什么牺牲的话就什么都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到什么东西 就需要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是炼金术的等价交换原则
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时我们坚信那就是世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fn华康雅艺体W6\pos(720,760)\3c&HD3CF9C&\fs70}国家炼金术师资格考试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}塔克是因在两年前炼成了能说人话的合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而获得国家炼金术师资格的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能说人话的合成兽?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以遗传上不同的两种或以上的的生物作为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炼成的合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是"合成的怪兽"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}据说能听懂人话 还能说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家里除了他以外 还有四岁的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有妻子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干什么呢 赶快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行啊 亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您就是…塔克先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家里没有主妇 乱成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 大哥哥的衣服真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不觉得重么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系的 哥哥我很有力气的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关于他们两个人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总有一天会有机会告诉您的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那之前就请您…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮娜去外边玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亚历山大会寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么等会见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想不到这样的年纪就立志成为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有我能办到的事 尽管提出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 我想看看塔克先生炼成的合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 在炼成后不久就死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么样 通过考试最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只凭一朝一夕的努力 是没法合格的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是资料室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请随便使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有好多好多没看过的书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里的资料跟国立中央图书馆比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是小巫见大巫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要考试合格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就能获得汲取比这多数十倍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 是数百倍的知识的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 要努…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德 学习还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 不知道的东西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是对受过特别教育的大人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那也是很困难的考试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过你还年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不一定非要坚持今年考的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 要尽可能试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论合格的可能性有多小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要能有所进展的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大哥哥什么都不吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好好吃饭可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看起来好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要慢慢吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 再来一块
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 学的东西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥你一定能通过考试的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以晚上就好好睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好怀念啊 这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们只是拼命地想要成为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觉得如果成功的话 前途就一定会明朗起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 你在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小哥哥 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥你们要是考完试后还一直呆在这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 你在画什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这叫"炼成阵"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是能达成愿望的魔咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害 好厉害 哥哥好厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天是爱德的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 你怎么会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底我也是调查部的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 到我家里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}内人在家等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边那位小淑女也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}庆祝生日还是大家都在一起才开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎 正等着你们来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是内人格蕾希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肚子好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要生小宝宝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上就要生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"好想快点出来呀"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像在里面边这么说边闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮娜想要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请吧 小妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 还要添茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格蕾希亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老公 马…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上要生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那那那那个 还没到预产期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…小宝宝好像已经要出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找医生 必须赶紧找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外面风雪交加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等着 我去找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我啊 格蕾希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思啊 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格蕾希亚阿姨 开水烧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢 请你放在地板上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 还需要很多的毛巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛巾是吧 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}医生好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 这么大的雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行了 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 格蕾希亚阿姨说要死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿姨啊 你不能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋 只不过是昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 从炼金术上考虑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果要创造出新的生命 就要付出相应的代价…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生小孩不是炼金术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要紧吧 格蕾希亚阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶 该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种时候什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 开水变凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 刚才你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么也没…连炼成阵也没画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那为什么水开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是精神啊 精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办才好啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}医生还不来吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生出来了 生出来了啊 格蕾希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多亏了大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的 真的谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们什么也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直陪在我旁边呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们虽说是炼金术师 可最后什么忙也没帮上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相比起来 母亲还真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能做到炼金术师花费几百年都没能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的妈妈也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:13:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我刚生出来的时候\N也是那样暖暖的 软乎乎的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之后 我们比以前更深入地钻研炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一心只想恢复与生俱来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说起来 哥哥之前居然没有画炼成阵就让水沸腾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个嘛 那时候比较特别啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算这样 哥哥也真厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也必须要努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧 我来出题考你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离考试的日子越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考试历年都是按照笔试 面试和实际操作的顺序进行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考生的人数虽然不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是能通过的每年只有一两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有这么点人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…面试的时候都干些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我面试的时候 只是一些问答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 因人而异 好像也有体检一类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}体检吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有 实际操作考试的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有像我这样把研究成果带去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也有要求在现场进行炼成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}五五之数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们怎么打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不妙啊 实际操作考试怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之前 要是得接受体检怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是被看到铠甲里面空荡荡的不就露馅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么嘛 穆斯唐中佐肯定会为我们想办法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们忐忑不安地 迎来了考试的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在开始进行笔试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥们 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都没能答到最后一题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我倒是做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过接下来是面试…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到弟弟也通过了笔试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}面试啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会…我不能接受!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是为什么 为什么我不能参加面试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你想隐藏过去继续向前的话 只能如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 我要和哥哥一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是挺好嘛 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}皮娜可婆婆说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}国家炼金术师这种家伙\N在战争的时候就会被派往前线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还可能使用本应为大众服务的炼金术来杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}合格就等于成为军队的走狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为国家炼金术师的只有我一个就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我一定要合格 然后达成你的愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黄金的三脚椅?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么那样子还能不倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你是真正的炼金术师 椅子就不会拒绝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炼金术师啊 无论何时都不能畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 能说说你参加考试的动机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为约定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我唯一的亲人约定了 一定要成为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 我们选择的道路是正确的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 我确定的只是 我想再摸一摸哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然一直相距这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是抚摸的感觉啦 身体的样子啦\N都完全记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后 到了实际操作考试那天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达成愿望的魔咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在开始 这片地里的所有物质都交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请自己随意进行炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是随意 到底怎么样才能合格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东西不错 但是耗尽体力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一个是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}树和水?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥他没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有妮娜的魔咒呢 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用树和水造出了纸和氢气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经可以不用炼成阵了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个非常年轻的炼金术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fn方正隶变_GBK\b1\pos(720,750)\fs60\c&H00DEE0DD}爱德华·艾尔利克 国家炼金术师资格考试
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我决定不再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停下来的话…那时候再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总有一天 我要让你恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时候要连哥哥的身体一起恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}合成兽恸哭之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮娜…
